Evaluation of Oyster exposure experiments

knitr::opts_chunk$set(echo = TRUE, warning = F, message = F, fig.path = 'figs/', dev.args = list(family = 'serif'))

library(tidyverse)
library(patchwork)
library(ggbeeswarm)
library(psycho)
library(lmerTest)
library(hrbrthemes)
library(kableExtra)
library(shiny)

source('R/funcs.R')

data(allres)
data(resmods)
data(reswksmods)
data(alldis)
data(dismods)
data(diswksmods)

Respiration

Raw data

p <- ggplot(allres, aes(x = factor(week), y = resp, colour = species, fill = species)) + 
  geom_boxplot(outlier.shape = NA, alpha = 0.1) + 
  geom_point(aes(group = species), position = position_jitterdodge(jitter.width = 0.1), size = 2, alpha = 0.6) + 
  theme_ipsum_rc() + 
  facet_grid(trt~ .) + 
  scale_colour_ipsum() + 
  scale_fill_ipsum() + 
  theme(legend.title = element_blank()) + 
  labs(x = 'Exposure week', y = 'Respiration (umol/hr/g)')

p

resmods %>%

Dissolution score

Raw data

yvar <- 'Dissolution score (0-3)'
toplo <- alldis %>% 
  filter(var %in% yvar)

p <- ggplot(toplo, aes(x = factor(week), y = val, colour = species, fill = species)) + 
  geom_boxplot(outlier.shape = NA, alpha = 0.1) + 
  geom_point(aes(group = species), position = position_jitterdodge(jitter.width = 0.1), size = 2, alpha = 0.6) + 
  theme_ipsum_rc() + 
  facet_grid(trt~ .) + 
  scale_colour_ipsum() + 
  scale_fill_ipsum() + 
  theme(legend.title = element_blank()) + 
  labs(x = 'Exposure week', y = yvar)
